author: Matthew Fryou
title: LSU fans looking forward to homecoming game against WKU
text:
BATON ROUGE, LA (WAFB) - LSU Fans are turning their attention from a somber victory against USC, to this Saturday's homecoming game against Western Kentucky.
The parade grounds were the scene for LSU's homecoming pep rally. The court, spirit squad, and tiger band were all there to show their school spirit.
A homecoming parade is scheduled for Saturday morning at 11:00 a.m.
The game against Western Kentucky is scheduled for 6:00 p.m. on Saturday on ESPN-U.
